OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F339A1784395091
OL,3,CWoman admits trying to murder two 10-
OL,4,Cyear-old boys
OL,6,FA woman who was previously deemed
OL,7,Funfit to stand trial has admitted
OL,8,Ftrying to stab two 10-year-old boys to
OL,9,Fdeath at a property in Lincolnshire.
OL,11,FAnn Marie McEvoy now 45, was arrested
OL,12,Fafter police found the boys with stab
OL,13,Fwounds at a flat in Fold Hill,
OL,14,FFriskney, near Skegness, on 30
OL,15,FNovember 2022.
OL,17,FShe was charged with attempted murder
OL,18,Fbut was deemed unfit to plead and
OL,19,Fdetained in a secure hospital after a
OL,20,Ftrial of facts found she had carried
OL,21,Fout the stabbings.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,340,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F339A1784395091
OL,3,CWoman admits trying to murder two 10-
OL,4,Cyear-old boys
OL,6,FBut on Thursday McEvoy, formerly of
OL,7,FChurch Walk, Colchester, appeared at
OL,8,FLincoln Crown Court after her
OL,9,Fcondition improved and admitted the
OL,10,Fcharges.
OL,12,FJudge Simon Hirst adjourned sentencing
OL,13,Funtil 18 September for the preparation
OL,14,Fof updated medical and psychiatric
OL,15,Freports.
OL,17,FHe told McEvoy: "You have pleaded
OL,18,Fguilty of course to serious matters. I
OL,19,Faccept at the time you had significant
OL,20,Fmental health problems.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,340,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F339A1784395091
OL,3,CWoman admits trying to murder two 10-
OL,4,Cyear-old boys
OL,6,F"At this stage I am not giving any
OL,7,Findication of what that sentence will
OL,8,Fbe."
OL,10,FMark Knowles, defending, said McEvoy
OL,11,Fwas willing to enter her guilty pleas
OL,12,Fas she did not want to put the
OL,13,Fchildren through anything more.
OL,15,FThe court was previously told how
OL,16,Fofficers were sent to the flat in
OL,17,FFriskney on the afternoon of 29
OL,18,FNovember 2022 after Essex officers
OL,19,Fvisited McEvoy's home in Colchester
OL,20,Fand found she was not there.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
