OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,340,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F339A1784395091
OL,3,CWoman admits trying to murder two 10-
OL,4,Cyear-old boys
OL,6,FThe court heard McEvoy brandished a
OL,7,Flarge knife when an officer went to
OL,8,Fthe front door of the flat at around
OL,9,F3.30pm and then refused entry to the
OL,10,Fproperty.
OL,12,FA number of officers and negotiators
OL,13,Fwere called to the scene and after a
OL,14,Fstand-off lasting several hours it was
OL,15,Fdecided firearms officers should force
OL,16,Fentry during the early hours of 30
OL,17,FNovember 2022.
OL,19,FThey found McEvoy in a room with a
OL,20,Flarge knife above her head.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,340,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F339A1784395091
OL,3,CWoman admits trying to murder two 10-
OL,4,Cyear-old boys
OL,6,FThe two boys were lying next to each
OL,7,Fother and had both suffered injuries
OL,8,Fwhich required hospital treatment.
OL,10,FMcEvoy was tasered and fell to the
OL,11,Fground while the two boys were taken
OL,12,Finto another room for medical
OL,13,Ftreatment and then to hospital.
OL,15,FOne of the boys had suffered a number
OL,16,Fof puncture wounds across his chest
OL,17,Fand a large wound to the centre of his
OL,18,Fback.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,340,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F339A1784395091
OL,3,CWoman admits trying to murder two 10-
OL,4,Cyear-old boys
OL,6,FThe other boy suffered an injury to
OL,7,Fhis neck which was located under his
OL,8,Fear and a deep injury to his left arm.
OL,10,FFollowing the incident both boys were
OL,11,Finterviewed by specially trained
OL,12,Fpolice officers.
OL,14,FOne of the boys described how McEvoy
OL,15,Finflicted the injuries just before
OL,16,Fpolice entered the property.
OL,18,FMcEvoy was arrested at the scene but
OL,19,Fdeclined to give an explanation during
OL,20,Fher police interview.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/6
